nodes.text: Wetsuits were articles of clothing worn for aquatic purposes. Bodyhugging affairs, they offered the wearer complete protection from water—with a wetsuit and a breath mask, oxygen-breathers could function underwater. Ket Maliss, Gyran, and other members of a mercenary team assembled by Black Sun's Prince Xizor in 3 ABY wore wetsuits while searching for the stolen Barani List in an underwater village on the planet Sedri.
